Package com.example.ihuntwithjavalins.QRCode

Class QRCodeDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.ihuntwithjavalins.QRCode.QRCodeDB
  • public class QRCodeDB
extends java.lang.Object
    QRCodeDB is a class which handles all database operations for QRCode objects. Much functionality is derived from Well Fed project example given by TA Design Patterns: factory pattern - DBConnection object defining db and collection observer pattern - Use of OnCompleteListener command pattern - addQRCode, getQRCode, and deleteCode all pass commands to QRCodeDB singleton pattern - use of getINstance to access the FirebaseFirestore object
